items.name: FoolKat GOD-OF-JOY
items.description:
This is the eighth model in my God series.

You can find all the models at GOD-OF-GREED, GOD-OF-ENVY, GOD-OF-LOVE, GOD-OF-ANIME, GOD-OF-LUST, GOD-OF-JUSTICE, GOD-OF-TIME, GOD-OF-FANTASY, GOD-OF-JOY, GOD-OF-HORROR, GOD-OF-PRIDE, GOD-OF-PUNK, GOD-OF-STORMS, GOD-OF-EUPHORIA, GOD-OF-GLUTTONY, GOD-OF-THE-WEST, GOD-OF-BEAUTY, GOD-OF-SEDUCTION, and GOD-OF-PEACE.

This model is a mix of Toonify Legacy, my FoolKat_GOD-OF-ENVY_V1 model, Thumbelina v2.0, and my FoolKat_GOD-OF-ANIME_V1 model, which was added to help with anatomy issues that happened in the beta model.

The model was mixed with some Lora files to produce a style with softer, rounder edges that brought out a sense of euphoria in me, so I decided to call it JOY.

The model has Blessed2 VAE baked into it, so no VAE required.

All of the images I upload for this model are unedited and don't use any special extensions like ControlNet. I do not do any inpainting or img2img to correct errors. Why? Because you deserve to see how the model works without any touchup or special extensions like ControlNet. You can surely get better images by putting in the extra work, which I do for my personal images. The samples are just meant to showcase what the model can do raw with nothing but prompt engineering.

items.name: Tinker Toys Reimagined
items.description:
I remember FONDLY the days of my childhood where everything was fresh, the world was yet to be discovered, and something as simple as 'Tinker Toys' were able to entertain me for hours on end. This is when I thought how cool would it be to explore Tinker Toys in a completely new age with endless possibilities. This LORA, in its initial phase, may not produce a perfect replica of this childhood classic but it sure is fun to work with. This LORA is fresh off the press and I am still trying to figure out all that it can do. I will try to post more images as I obtain them. Enjoy 👽

If this LORA were a steak it might be medium rare to medium. Meaning, might need to pump up the weight a bit but most models so far seem to tolerate the extra spice.

Edit2: This LORA seems pretty flexible. Placing earlier in prompt seems to emphasize the elements better. Try adding phrases like 'toy', 'playful', 'toys', even try with and with out the key word 'tinker toys' for more emphasis. IT also seems to be decent at realistic photo styles and can add interesting color schemes to photos/images.

items.name: Nisino2222 Style
items.description:
A colorful artistic style specialized mainly in portraits

How to use
While no trigger word is required I highly recommend using "simple background" or, preferably, any color background tag.

On AOM2 and any other model with realism mixed in I also recommend adding "3d" and/or "realistic" to the negative tags for best performance.
Content this model is good at are portraits as mentioned, upper body shots, close-ups, androgynous boys and themes from the Berserk manga. The LoRA is a bit unstable, you may occasionally get nightmarish fleshpile monstrosities but I still felt like sharing it since when it works it works very well IMHO.

For prompt tips please see the sample images or the uploaded zip of training tags.

As usual all images are raw, slightly cherrypicked, txt2img gens, no inpainting or helper embeddings used.

MISC
Trained on NAI at 512 resolution with a dataset of 80 images.
The training was done on a small subset of the artists images, as such the output of this LoRA is not an accurate representation neither in quality or style of the source material. Go support the artist Nisino22222 if you want the good stuff.

items.name: ZavyComics
items.description:
Come join my Discord!

This model will always remain publicly available for download. It is important to note that full exclusivity will never be considered.

If you have any commercial proposals or are interested in engaging in commercial activities beyond simply selling images created with the model, I encourage you to contact me through Discord. I am open to further discussions and exploring potential collaborations in these areas.
Updates 
14/07/2023: Inpainting model released based on ZavyComics_b1.

Introduction

Many anime/comic models available here tend to have a harsh and highly detailed style with thin outlines, which may not be to everyone's preference. Therefore, I have specifically focused on addressing these three aspects in this model to reach a more authentic looking anime/comic style. The output it generates consists of softer and flatter images with thicker outlines. This particular style makes it relatively easy to edit areas that may not meet your liking with basic knowledge of image editing tools. Consequently, it becomes easier to shape an image according to your desired vision using img2img.

I kindly request that you share your creations both here and on my Discord server, as I would greatly appreciate the opportunity to see them.

Pros and cons

Pros

  • Excels in anatomically correct fingers and toes.

  • Produces impressive results without relying on terms like "masterpiece" or "best quality" prompts. This allows for a more efficient use of token space in the prompts, enabling clearer and more effective instructions to guide the image creation process according to your specific vision.

  • Produces images with minimal artifacting and random smudges. The resulting outputs are cleaner and exhibit fewer undesired visual distortions.

  • The images generated by this model have a noticeably soft appearance. The output tends to have a gentle and smooth quality, which can contribute to a more soothing and aesthetically pleasing visual experience.

  • The flatter image style produced by this model makes it easier to edit as there is less colour complexity in the gradients. The reduced presence of gradients simplifies the editing process, allowing for more straightforward adjustments to achieve the desired outcome.

  • The emphasis on thick outlines enhances the visual style, giving the artwork a distinct and recognizable appearance commonly seen in traditional anime and comic illustrations.

  • This model is highly receptive to various levels of detail, allowing you to adjust the complexity (with detail enhancing LORAs especially) of the image according to your preferences.

  • This model excels in producing exceptional results when generating grayscale manga-style images.

Cons

  • In certain cases, the image style can be significantly influenced by certain LORAs, resulting in a harsher appearance that deviates from the intended softness of this model. To address this, techniques such as block weighting or utilizing img2img can be employed to restore the desired softness and bring the image closer to the original intent of the model.

  • The model occasionally generates jagged-looking pupils, which may require manual editing to achieve a more accurate and visually pleasing appearance.

Roadmap

  1. In-painting model release. Done.

  2. Update the model to minimise some of its drawbacks and incorporate a more current blend of models. Done.

  3. Model inspired by anime and comic styles. Done.

  4. SDXL models.

  5. Pioneering uncharted LORA subjects (withholding specifics to prevent preemption)

Tips

  • To better understand the preferences of the model, individuals are encouraged to utilise the provided prompts as a foundation and then customise, modify, or expand upon them according to their desired objectives.

  • Avoid using face restoration techniques as they are often unnecessary and can lead to inferior results compared to the original model.

  • Consider utilising Dynamic Thresholding as a method to control CFG. This technique can help you get improved results.

  • If you find that the details in your work are lacking, consider using adetailer (or similar LORA) if you’re unable to fix it with prompt alone. Adetailer or similar tools can enhance and enrich the level of detail, but in turn it will lose some of the softness intended by this model.

  • For even better LORA results, make use of the LORA block weighting. By incorporating that, you can further enhance the outcome and achieve superior results in the LORA process.

  • Avoid using underscores in your prompt, unless part of the trigger word for a LORA.

  • To maintain optimal results and avoid excessive duplication of subjects, limit the generated image size to a maximum of 768x768 pixels or 768x1024 pixels (or vice versa). If you require higher resolutions, it is recommended to utilise the Hires fix, followed by the img2img upscale technique, with particular emphasis on the controlnet tile upscale method. This approach will help you achieve superior results when aiming for higher resolution outputs.

Prompts and TI

No specific positive or negative prompts are specifically recommended for this model. It functions well as a base without relying on any particular type of prompt. You have the freedom to mix and match prompts according to your preferences, increasing or decreasing their influence in the direction you desire. This flexibility allows you to experiment and customise the output to your liking, shaping the image generation process to align with your creative vision.

For negative prompts, consider employing Textual Inversion techniques. The following are recommended: easynegative, bad_prompt, and badhandv4. However, there are other TI available that potentially yield better results. Feel free to experiment with different TI and share your findings!

Recommended settings

  • Vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.vae. (Other more anime oriented ones like blessed2.vae work well too).

  • Euler A.

  • Steps 30~40 (can go lower with DPM++ 2M Karras, but I’ve found Euler A to make a more pleasing image).

  • Hires upscaler: 4x_foolhardy_Remacri or 4x-UltraSharp depending on image.

  • Hires upscale: Whatever maximum your GPU is capable of, but preferably between 1.5x~2x.

  • CFG scale 4-8 (unless you use Dynamic Thresholding).

  • Clip skip 2.

Model recipe

The recipe for the model is quite complex, as it involves utilising different weight settings for each individual input and output layer in each model used in the mixture. Consequently, the following instructions may not yield results that closely resemble this specific model. However, the fundamental recipe is as follows:

Model A:
duchaitenLofi
Model B:
realcartoon3d
Model C:
kidsmix_v10

Model A:
ZavyComics_a1
Model B:
childrenStories_v13D
Model C:
flat2DAnimerge_v30

I would like to express my gratitude to the creators of the models incorporated in this mixture, as well as the creators of the models that came before them.

Social media

You are welcome to join my recently created Discord server (it’s not very active yet, I’ll ramp up activity there with SDXL), where we can engage in discussions, share our experiences in AI, and showcase the things we’ve made with AI. You are encouraged to join and ask any questions or seek additional tips and tricks related to my models or AI in general. Your participation would be greatly appreciated. Furthermore, I will be releasing early testing versions of my models on Discord. If you are interested in being among the first to try them out, I invite you to join the Discord server.

items.description:
基于 90 张小鹏 XPeng G6 外观图片，以 720x720 分辨率训练的 LoRA。

触发词（trigger words）为：XPeng G6, a car。权重（weights）推荐 0.6-1.0，如果泛化不佳可适当降低权重，但低于 0.6 将使造成出现比较明显的瑕疵。

训练图片主要基于“熔云橙”和“新月银”两种颜色，也使用了其他几种颜色的图片，但由于数量不如前两种颜色，出图是颜色可能会不太准确。特别是“星雨青”和“星阙灰”。具体颜色对应的 trigger words 如下：

熔云橙：XPeng G6, an orange car

新月银：XPeng G6, a silver car

星云白：XPeng G6, a white car

光子蓝：XPeng G6, a blue car

星阙灰：XPeng G6, a gray car

星雨青：XPeng G6, a green car

如果要生成 1920x1080 图片，可以 960x540 生成图片，再使用“高清修复（Hires. fix）”进行 2 倍放大。

这是群星再世第三十一期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

高仓健，日本著名影星，在70年代末期，其参演的影片《追捕》进入到中国市场，以“硬汉”的形象，迅速在中国收获了一众粉丝，更是有粉丝在他电影主页评价到：“好一个东瀛的硬汉，用《追捕》迷倒了我妈，用《网走番高地》吸引了我爸，用《新干线爆炸案》惊住了我，最后用《铁道员》让我们一家哭得稀里哗啦。您80大寿的时候说要演新电影，其实我们只希望您注意身体，长命百岁。”

寥寥数语，概括出了高仓健不同的荧幕形象，对那代中国人来讲，高仓健不是演员，也不是某个具体角色，而是一种形象，这个形象包括了勇气、忠诚、坚毅面孔、沉默寡言的性格，以及荒原上骑马奔逐的身影。


2014年高仓健因病去世，享年83岁，其遗产被“养女”侵吞变卖，骨灰撒入大海。

“一语道尽是遗憾”，杜丘，你看，多么蓝的天，一直往前走，不要往两边看，你将会融化在蓝天里。

https://t.me/+Vm8qxYr2QYgxMjJl 我的群组

高倉健、日本の有名な映画スター、70年代の終わりに、彼の出演した映画『追捕』は中国市場に入って、「硬骨漢」のイメージで、急速に中国で多くのファンを収獲しました。「すごい日本の硬骨漢で、『追捕』で私の母を魅了して、『網走番高地』で私の父を魅了して、『新幹線爆破事件』で私を驚かせて、最後に『鉄道員(ぽっぽや)』で私たちの家族を泣かせました。80歳の誕生日を迎え、新しい映画に出演すると言いましたが、体に気をつけて長生きしてほしいだけです」

その世代の中国人にとって、高倉健は俳優でもなく、具体的なキャラクターでもなく、一種のイメージです。このイメージには勇気、忠誠心、毅然とした顔、寡黙な性格、そして荒野で馬に乗って疾走する姿が含まれています。

2014年に83歳で病気で亡くなり、遺産は「養女」に横領されて売却され、遺灰は海に撒かれました。

「残念なことばかり言っています」杜丘、見て、なんて青い空なんだろう、まっすぐに進んで、両側を見ないで、あなたは青空に溶けてしまいます。

items.name: Ichika Matsumoto
items.description:
Ichika Matsumoto is a Japanese AV actress.

Training includes several nudes. Gets nsfw easily. You may want to use "(nude:2)" or something similar as a negative prompt.

In my experience, many "realistic" models struggle to depict her face accurately. Depending on the model, you may need to do some tweaking before you get good results.

She likes to wear a maid outfit by default.

She is friends with Yui Nagase.

See more pictures of her on my DeviantArt page.

(Note that some of the sample pictures here were created with a fewer-training-steps version. I'm happy to upload it if anybody needs it.)
